{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297110/extras/AnemorieAboutThisBanner.gif?t=1733678662\" /><i><strong>Anemorie</strong></i> is a visually captivating, story-driven adventure set in the 1990s, where you step into the life of Anna\u2014a young woman navigating the complexities of self-discovery, love, and resilience. Living with a heart condition, Anna possesses a unique gift: the ability to glimpse memories embedded in cherished objects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297110/extras/AnemorieAssetsBanner01.gif?t=1733678662\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297110/extras/AnemorieGameFeaturesBanner.gif?t=1733678662\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>\ud83c\udf3b Narrative-Rich Gameplay</strong></i>: Immerse yourself in an emotional journey as Anna confronts her past, explores her supernatural abilities, and forges meaningful relationships.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>\ud83c\udf3b Thematic Mini-Games</strong></i><strong>:</strong> Engage in unique, context-specific mini-games that reflect Anna's experiences and challenges, offering deeper insight into her world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>\ud83c\udf3b Daily Activities</strong>:</i> Assist Anna with her daily routines\u2014from cooking breakfast and journaling to bonding with her beloved cat, Kohi\u2014each activity revealing more about her character and story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>\ud83c\udf3b And so much more</strong></i>\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297110/extras/AnemorieAssetsBanner02.gif?t=1733678662\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://sh